#homesteadmath #hrcemath Using a numberline to add
🤔124+31=?
🤔What do I know?
👍31 is 3 jumps of 10 and 1 more
👍I start at 124 and make 3 jumps of 10 and a small jump of 1
124➡134➡144➡154➡155
😃124+31=155
🤔How else could you show this on a number line? https://t.co/ikQmHNSPBn
